text: Kasimovka () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Verkhnestaritskoye Rural Settlement, Gaynsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 428 as of 2010. There are 11 streets. == Geography == It is located 3 km south from Verkhnyaya Staritsa. == References == Category:Rural localities in Gaynsky District
title: Kasimovka
